channel.title: 667 Poanizer Project error ~HELP!~
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape Community!
I know this is the 2nd time I make a post about an error today (the other one being a devilscape error, go in client help and it should be there if you wanna check it out :P ). Ok so now I'm on a 667 Project Poanizer source and I got this weird error about an ip which is 0.0.0.0 and I can't seem to find it anywhere!(I searched in source & Client). I read the error (like EVERY SINGLE comment on moparscape) and I can' find it (0.0.0.0). What I found is 127.0.0.1 which is local host and normal so I don't why I get the error. Thanks for helping and if you take a look at the source by yourself, my skype is sakoofortin and then we could teamviewer/screen sharing. Thanks! Btw I'm new to 667 ;) ****FIXED**** I just saw that the port 43594 was open on utorrent so I just had to close it :D
